Garret Orbach is a member of B. Riley’s Investment Banking Group responsible for the evaluation and analysis of public and private company transactions, including mergers and acquisitions, equity and debt financings. He joined B. Riley from j2 Global, Inc. (Nasdaq: JCOM), a Los Angeles-based highly acquisitive cloud services and digital media company. His experience includes financial planning and budgeting procedures as well as analysis of acquisition targets, synergy potential and financial modeling.

Mr. Orbach is an accelerated graduate from the University of California Los Angeles where he received a B.A. in Economics.
